\[H(e^{j\omega})\,=\,\frac{2}{1-\frac{3}{4}e^{-j\omega}+\frac{1}{8}e^{-j2\omega}}. \tag{5.85}\]

As a first step in obtaining the impulse response, we factor the denominator of eq. (5.85):

